      <i> ♪ Students learning</i>
        <i> from the best! ♪</i>

247
00:11:22,082 --> 00:11:25,717
     <i> ♪ Taking notes to pass</i>
      <i> the test! ♪</i>

248
00:11:25,819 --> 00:11:29,020
 <i> ♪ Wait hold on! Not like that,</i>
