00:11:33,193 --> 00:11:34,827
<i>♪ Yup! Right here in the book ♪</i>

252
00:11:35,028 --> 00:11:37,562
       <i> ♪ Come on!</i>
  <i> We just got in the groove! ♪</i>

253
00:11:38,765 --> 00:11:41,800
     <i> ♪ Can't mess up</i>
